** ERR
LOCATION REQUIRED.
DATE ERROR
FROM DATE > TODAY'S DATE.
FROM DATE > TO DATE.
NO DATA FOUND!
DATA OVER LIMIT! CHANGE SELECT CONDITION THEN TRY AGAIN.
PAGE# VALID WITH LOT#.



